<div class="main_body_subhead orng_text">Kroogi Mark-up</div>
Use these tools to add more to your text entries.<br /><br />

<div class="main_body_subhead">Kroogi Names</div>
Enter <b>&lt;kroogi user="kroogi name" &#47;&gt;</b> to show a link to a user/project's Kroogi Page.<br />
<b><i>Example</i></b><br />
Enter <b>&lt;kroogi user="user-forum" &#47;&gt;</b><br />
Get <a href="user-forum">user-forum</a><br /><br />

Enter <b>&lt;kroogi user="kroogi name"&gt; Any text &lt;/kroogi&gt;</b> to show a link to a user/project's Kroogi Page hidden under other text.<br />
<b><i>Example</i></b><br />
Enter <b>&lt;kroogi user="user-forum"&gt; Kroogi User Forum &lt;/kroogi&gt;</b><br />
Get <a href="user-forum"> Kroogi User Forum </a><br /><br />

<div class="main_body_subhead">Titles</div>
Use <b>&lt;h1&gt;</b> - <b>&lt;h6&gt;</b> to display headers.<br />
<b><i>Example</i></b><br />
Enter <b>&lt;h3&gt;Header Title&lt;/h3&gt;</b><br />
Get <span style="font-size:13px; font-weight:bold;">Header Title</span><br /><br />

<div class="main_body_subhead">Images</div>
Use <b>&lt;img&gt;</b> tags to display images from other sites.<br />
<b><i>Example</i></b><br />
Enter <b>&lt;img src="http://www.google.com/intl/en_ALL/images/logo.gif"&gt;</b> and get:<br />
<img src="http://www.google.com/intl/en_ALL/images/logo.gif"><br /><br />

To include showcase image to your entry, right click on the image of desired size (small, bigger or download) get image location and enter it into the <b>&lt;img&gt;</b> tag.<br />
<b><i>Example</i></b><br />
Enter <b>&lt;img src="http://s3.amazonaws.com/krugi/content/thumbs/2735/orn2_big.jpg"&gt;</b> and get:<br /><br />
<img src="http://s3.amazonaws.com/krugi/content/thumbs/2735/orn2_big.jpg"><br /><br />

<div class="main_body_subhead">Text</div>
Use <b>&lt;i&gt;, &lt;b&gt;, &lt;u&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;, &lt;em&gt;</b> to show text as <i>italic</i>, <b>bold</b>, <u>underlined</u>, <strong>strong</strong>, <em>emphasized</em>.<br /><br />

<div class="main_body_subhead">Lists</div>
Use <b>&lt;ul&gt;</b> and <b>&lt;li&gt;</b>, to show bulleted lists.<br />
<b><i>Example</i></b><br />
Enter:<br />
<b>&lt;ul&gt;<br />
&lt;li&gt;Option 1&lt;/li&gt;<br />
&lt;li&gt;Option 2&lt;/li&gt;<br />
&lt;li&gt;Option 3&lt;/li&gt;<br />
&lt;/ul&gt;</b><br />
Get:
<ul>
<li>Option 1</li>
<li>Option 2</li>
<li>Option 3</li>
</ul>
Use <b>&lt;ol&gt;</b> and <b>&lt;li&gt;</b>, to show numbered lists.<br />

<b><i>Example</i></b><br />
Enter:<br />
<b>&lt;ol&gt;<br />
&lt;li&gt;Option 1&lt;/li&gt;<br />
&lt;li&gt;Option 2&lt;/li&gt;<br />
&lt;li&gt;Option 3&lt;/li&gt;<br />
&lt;/ol&gt;</b><br />
Get:
<ol>
<li>Option 1</li>
<li>Option 2</li>
<li>Option 3</li>
</ol><br />

<div class="main_body_subhead">Embed Media</div>
Use <b>&lt;embed&gt;</b> tag to embed media from other sites (Note: some video hosting sites are not supported due to security issues). You can use YouTube and RuTube to host your videos. If you use other services, make sure that your video can actually be played after you post it.<br /><br />

<b><i>Example</i></b><br /><br />
<object width="425" height="344"><param name="movie" value="http://www.youtube.com/v/6gmP4nk0EOE"></param><param name="wmode" value="transparent"></param><embed src="http://www.youtube.com/v/6gmP4nk0EOE" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" wmode="transparent" width="425" height="344"></embed></object><br /><br /><br />

<div class="main_body_subhead">Some Standard HTML still works</div>
For example (without quotes): "&lt;a href=&quot;http://kroogi.ru/explore&quot;&gt;http://kroogi.ru/explore&lt;/a&gt;"
produces: <a href="http://kroogi.ru/explore/">http://kroogi.ru/explore/</a><br /><br />
