<div class="main_body_subhead orng_text">Facebook Kroogi Downloads Tutorial</div>
It's easy for both artists and fans to promote and share Kroogi music on Facebook.<br /><br />
<div class="main_body_subhead">For Artists</div>

Any public Facebook account can be used to promote Kroogi artists by adding a Kroogi Downloads tab/box to your profile. When people click on it, they'll see a list of albums you've downloaded using our Facebook application.<br /><br />

<b>Adding a Kroogi Tab to Your Personal Profile:</b><br /><br />

1. Go to our <a href="http://apps.facebook.com/kroogidownloads/" target="_blank">application page</a>.<br /><br />
2. On the right-hand side of the page, you'll see a box that says, "Promote your favorite artists and share your tastes with your friends!" There is an "Add to Profile" link inside. Click on it to add the box.<br /><br />

Artists can promote their project with a Kroogi tab on their Facebook fan page. When people click on the tab, they'll see links to your Kroogi Downloads profile and your albums.<br /><br />

<div class="main_body_subhead">For Fans: Choosing an Artist to Represent on Facebook</div>

You can now use the Kroogi Downloads (KD) tab to represent one Kroogi artist of your choice on your Facebook profile.<br /><br />


1. Add the Kroogi Downloads (KD) tab to your Facebook page by going to the <a href="http://apps.facebook.com/kroogidownloads/" target="_blank">KD application page</a>.<br /><br />

2. Go back to your profile and click on your KD tab (tabs are located above your status)- to the right of your albums you'll see a link saying, You can now present artists from Kroogi and their albums on your profile. Click here to start." Click it.<br /><br />

3. When you go to your page and select the KD tab, you will be directed to a screen asking you, "What Kroogi Artist Do You Want to Represent?" Search for and select an artist (or yourself, if you're a musician on Kroogi). Then, write an introduction about the project you pick.<br /><br />

4. When other people click on your KD tab, they will see your description of the project, the project's name/picture, and a list of their albums available for download.<br /><br />

<b>For Facebook Fan Pages:</b><br /><br />

1. Add the KD tab to your Facebook page by going to the KD application page. A window will pop up, asking you to select which page you want to add the application to. Select your artist page.<br /><br />

2. When you go to your page and select the KD tab, you will be directed to a screen asking you, "What Kroogi Artist Do You Want to Represent?" Search for and select an artist (or yourself, if you are a musician on Kroogi). You will be able to write an introduction about the project you pick.<br /><br />

3. When other people click on you KD tab, they will see your description of the project, the project's name/picture, and a list of their albums that can be downloaded through Kroogi.<br /><br />
